data.description: Ladies and Gentlemen, I present to you...227 Big Oak Lane! Welcome home! This beautiful, one level, home has it all! Love to entertain? This home is perfect for that! You'll love the huge kitchen that flows into the family room and large dining area. The covered patio and outdoor bar area are perfect for days when you're lounging by the saltwater pool! The large workshop out back is sure to WOW! Previously used a cabinet workshop, it's already piped for your air compressor and is heated by a wood burning heater.  Don't miss this out on this beautiful home. Call your favorite agent today!
